    Step 8 of 8
    =20

    Exercise 6 : Upload to GitHub and submit the github pages URL = for peer review.

    When you are done with all the changes in the project, commit and push t= o GitHub. You do not have to create a Push Request back to the original IBM= repository.

    If you need to refresh your memory on how to commit and push to GitHub i= n Theia lab environment, please refer to this lab Working with git in the Theia lab env= ironment

    Open the URL of your project in a browser. (You created this URL in Exer= cise 1)

    You should see your completed project.

    Submit this URL for peer review.
